name: Weight Lifting
about: Weight training is a common type of strength training for developing the strength and size of skeletal muscles.

name: Hunter Barrera
about: The push-up (sometimes called a press-up in British English) is a common calisthenics exercise beginning from the prone position.

name: Jogging
about: Jogging is a form of trotting or running  intention is to increase physical fitness with less stress on the body.

name: Shoulder Taps
about: If performing shoulder taps from the high-plank position is a bit much for you right now to come down to knees.

name: Squats
about: A squat is a strength exercise in which the trainee lowers their hips from a standing position and then stands back up.

name: Abdominal Crunched
about: The crunch is an abdominal exercise that works the rectus abdominis muscle. It enables both building six-pack abs and tightening the belly.
